The Scenario Documentation section of reports contain one section for each of the scenario groups defined in a model (if any). For each of these groups, the following information is shown (for each scenario):
-included scenarios;
-start/end points;
-variable initialization;
-preconditions;
-postconditions.

If some of these fields are empty, the corresponding subsection(s) is/are not shown in the reports.

The Scenario Documentation section of reports is shown on the same page as the scenario execution summary. This section will not be present in reports if the "Show scenario information" preference was unchecked (on the Report Generation Preferences page).

